'''Galactic Capital Bank''' was located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It contained an account for the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] contributed by friends of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. In [[29 BBY/Legends|29 BBY]], three billion [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] was only a few percent of the total Jedi account.

